cast.overview: After their late former Captain is framed, Lowrey and Burnett try to clear his name, only to end up on the run themselves.
cast.title: Bad Boys: Ride or Die

details.biography:
Khabane "Khaby" Lame (French: [kabi lamei], Italian: [ˈkaːbi ˈlamei]; born March 9, 2000) is a Senegalese-Italian social media personality. He is known for his TikTok videos, in which he silently mocks overly complicated "life hack" videos.

In 2022, he was listed in Fortune's 40 Under 40 and Forbes' 30 Under 30.

He also served as a juror on the 2023 edition of the television show Italia's Got Talent.
details.name: Khaby Lame
